49/https://ohiostatepress.org/Books/Book%20PDFs/Harris%20Policing.pdf" id="mwBIY">Policing the City: Crime and Legal Authority in London, 1780–1840</a></i> PDF. Columbus: Ohio State University Press, 2004, 6. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt153" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"0-8142-0966-1"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBIc"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt153" id="mwBIg">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt153" id="mwBIk"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/0-8142-0966-1" title="Special:BookSources/0-8142-0966-1" about="#mwt153" id="mwBIo">0-8142-0966-1</a></span></li><li about="#cite_note-51" id="cite_note-51"><a href="./Police#cite_ref-51" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-51" class="mw-reference-text">Marjie Bloy, "<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.victorianweb.org/history/chad1.html" id="mwBIs">Edwin Chadwick (1800–1890)</a>," The Victorian Web.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-52" id="cite_note-52"><a href="./Police#cite_ref-52" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-52" class="mw-reference-text">Quoted in H.S. Cooper, "The Evolution of Canadian Police." In eds., W.T. McGrath and M.P. Mitchell, <i id="mwBIw">The Police Function in Canada</i>. Toronto: Methuen, 1981, 39. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt157" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"0-458-93920-X"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBI0"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Numb