U's probes"</a>. <i id="mwBWA">Toronto Star</i>. February 22, 2011.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Toronto+Star&amp;rft.atitle=Star+Exclusive%3A+Police+ignore+SIU%27s+probes&amp;rft.date=2011-02-22&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestar.com%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F943363--star-exclusive-police-ignore-siu-s-probes&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APolice" class="Z3988" about="#mwt487" id="mwBWE"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt487" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwBWI"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-98" id="cite_note-98"><a href="./Police#cite_ref-98" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-98" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation news" about="#mwt489" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite news","href":"./Template:Cite_news"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"https://www.nytimes.com/roomfordebate/2013/10/22/should-police-wear-cameras/body-cameras-could-restore-trust-in-police"},"work":{"wt":"The New York Times"},"title":{"wt":"If Police Encounters Were Filmed"},"date":{"wt":"October 22, 2013"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBWM"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://www.nytimes.com/roomfordebate/2013/10/22/should-police-wear-cameras/body-cameras-could-restore-trust-in-police" id="mwBWQ">"If Police Encounters Were Filmed"</a>. <i id="mwBWU">The New York Times</i>. October 22, 2013.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+New+York+Times&amp;rft.atitle=If+Police+Encounters+Were+Filmed&amp;rft.date=2013-10-22&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Froomfordebate%2F2013%2F10%2F22%2Fs